I can't generate audio files. I don't have text-to-speech capabilities. You can use tools like:

- **ElevenLabs** (elevenlabs.io)
- **Google Cloud Text-to-Speech**
- **gTTS** (Python library)
- **Edge TTS** (Python library)

Example with gTTS:
```bash
pip install gtts
python -c "from gtts import gTTS; tts = gTTS('NÓS SOMOS LEGENDÁRIOS, SEGUIMOS PELOS QUATRO CANTOS', lang='pt'); tts.save('audio.mp3')"
```
